  "title": "Business Development Executive (Tuas, M&E & Building Services)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Prepare and deliver technical proposals and presentations tailored to client requirements.</li><li>Develop and maintain strong, long-term client relationships across projects.</li><li>Collaborate with engineering teams to ensure solutions meet technical standards and project timelines.</li><li>Manage quotations, tenders, and contract negotiations while providing after-sales support.</li><li>Track industry trends and represent the company at trade shows, conferences, and client site visits.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma in Civil, Mechanical, Material Science, or equivalent</li><li>At least 2 years of sales experience in <strong>construction, building, or M&E consultancy industries.</strong></li><li>Strong presentation, communication, and interpersonal skills with customer-centric mindset.</li><li>Results-driven, self-disciplined, and able to manage multiple services/projects simultaneously.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
